		<title>Hot vs. Cold Leads (+How to Manage Every Type)</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/hot-leads-vs-cold-leads</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Ehtisham Hussain]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
